Titolo: The Forgotten Realms Archives

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: The Forgotten Realms Archives is a compilation of the AD&D Forgotten Realms series from the beginning of the series in 1988 through 1996, including 12 complete games:

The first Gold Box series:
Pool of Radiance;
Hillsfar;
Curse of the Azure Bonds;
Secret of the Silver Blades;
Pools of Darkness;
The Dungeon Master clones series:
Eye of the Beholder I;
Eye of the Beholder II: The Legend of Darkmoon;
Eye of the Beholder III: Assault on Myth Drannor;
Dungeon Hack;
Part of the second Gold Box series:
Gateway to the Savage Frontier;
Treasures of the Savage Frontier;
And also:
Menzoberranzan
A demo version of  Blood & Magic, including the source code.It was released in April 1997, and re-released a year later as a Silver Edition, which included an interactive demo for 1998's Baldur's Gate, and republished in 2001 as part of the Gamefest Interplay collector's series, Gamefest: Forgotten Realms Classics.

Genere: Non specificato


Valutazione: N/A
